nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: A slow, predatory dolly-in pushes through the shimmering heat haze of a deserted, sun-bleached gas station in the middle of nowhere. A beautiful, dangerous girl is leaning back against the hood of a vintage, cherry-red muscle car, a bead of condensation from her cold soda bottle tracing a path down her toned stomach. She is wearing a frayed, oil-stained, and ridiculously short cutoff tank top. As she tilts her head back to take a long, slow swallow, the camera captures the magnificent, undeniable truth: her top reveals her underboob, a glorious, sun-kissed proclamation in the vast, empty, and beautifully desolate silence.

nodes.title: Subject and Scene setup
widgets_values:
Setup is the same for both nodes. 

Person is set up for WAN 2.1

Scene is set up for WAN 2.2

```
Person text file format 
(For this example, the LoRA for the person is in the models\loras\person\ folder)

person\wan_2.1_LoraName.safetensors
#
bodytype\wan_2.1_LoraName.safetensors
#
Person description/prompt and any trigger words for the LoRAs.

```

```
Scene text file format 
(For this example, the LoRA for the position is in the models\loras\position\ folder)

position\wan_2.2_LoraName_High.safetensors
#
position\wan_2.1_LoraName_Low.safetensors
#
LoRA prompt and any trigger words for the LoRAs.

```

nodes.title: Custom node links
widgets_values:
[Comfy-ui-textsplit now available in custom nodes in Comfy](https://github.com/vsaan212/Vsaan212-workflow-utilities)


Folder setup for SubjectFiles and ComfyUI_ScenarioSelector

```
your-comfyui-root/
â””â”€ custom_nodes/
   â””â”€ comfyui-scenario-selector/
      â”œâ”€ __init__.py          # the node implementation
      â””â”€ ScenarioFiles/        # put your .txt files here
         â”œâ”€ city_walk.txt
         â”œâ”€ studio_portrait.txt
         â””â”€ beach_evening.txt
```
```
your-comfyui-root/
â””â”€ custom_nodes/
   â””â”€ ComfyUI_subjectselector/
      â”œâ”€ __init__.py          # the node implementation
      â””â”€ SubjectFiles/        # put your .txt files here
         â”œâ”€ woman1.txt
         â”œâ”€ woman2.txt
         â””â”€ woman1.txt
```
Setup:
should find Vsaan212-workflow-utilities but if not search in comfyui for that node and install. 

Manual:
download/clone the custom nodes and place it in your comfyui custom nodes folder. 
No install needed.

folders for the scenario and SubjectFiles and a bypass text with example formatting should be included
